(45, 1, '2014-05-29 11:57:46', '2014-05-29 11:57:46', '<div class="services-break"></div>\n<section style="grid grid-pad">\n	<aside class="services-col col-1-3">\n		<div class="service-icon">\n			<div class="icon-inner"><img src="http://wizard.technology/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/build-maintenance-300x300.png" alt="build-maintenance" /></div>\n		</div>\n		<h1>Bespoke</h1>\n		<p class="services-copy">Are you looking to attract more business, or perhaps save time and money? Yes? Great! We specialise in the build and maintenance of premium websites and custom apps designed to drive more traffic to your door. We also design and create professional web applications for you or your employees that save your valuable resources. We deliver a full range of personalised or unique solutions, designed to provide the highest value and benefit to the success of your business. </p>\n	</aside>\n	<aside class="services-col col-1-3">\n		<div class="service-icon">\n			<div class="icon-inner"><img src="http://wizard.technology/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/devices1-300x300.png" alt="devices" /></div>\n		</div>\n		<h1>Online</h1>\n		<p class="services-copy">Today''s internet provides massive potential benefits for your business. Make sure you can reach out to your customers! With devices including mobile phones, tablet and desktop computers, Wizard Technology can design and build compelling, search engine optimised (<abbr title="Search Engine Optimization">SEO</abbr>) user experiences that all of your customers can love! And with plenty of experience in social media integration, we ensure you fully unlock the power of exposure on sites like Twitter and Facebook.</p>\n	</aside>\n	<aside class="services-col col-1-3">\n		<div class="service-icon">\n			<div class="icon-inner"><img src="http://wizard.technology/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/communication-300x300.png" alt="communication" /></div>\n		</div>\n		<h1>Solutions</h1>\n		<p class="services-copy">Our mission is to create bespoke online <em>solutions</em>. Talk with us about your objectives. We make sure we understand the problem, design a solution closely with you, build and implement, and then monitor results to see if we can improve it. We love change. We understand that requirements may change any time after project initiation. We understand development methodologies, and know that no two projects are the same. We start each project with a blank canvas and tailor a process to suit you and your project. We''re here to <em>help</em> you.\n</p>\n	</aside>\n</section>', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-05-29 11:57:46', '2014-05-29 11:57:46', '', 6, 'http://wizard.technology/6-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
